llama.cpp (9190+dfsg-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  The earlier alternatives-based UI management has been replaced by a
  debconf-based solution. The default UI option is SimpleChat, a legacy theme.
  The recommended option is to download the UI from upstream. It is fully open
  source, but we cannot it build it in Debian (yet) because of missing
  dependencies.

